## 🧪 Running Tests

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"

pytest                                  # all tests
pytest --cov=pykworldsim               # with coverage report
pytest tests/test_simulation.py -v     # single module
pytest -k "test_physics"               # filter by name
```

